72,"uid":102701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"64gb夠用，但個mon唔夠用呢,愈用得耐就覺得個mon太窄，上網睇野或睇漫畫都好唔方便，放係枱度用faceid解鎖，角度斜多少少已解唔到，以往用開plus，，iphonex真係唔覺俾到咩驚喜我，而家我都考慮緊trade走部x換返7plus或轉note8"},{"pid":"1b10d90ea36d959dde9959408fefc68650d54134","tid":469872,"uid":872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你老母cap screen唔會有m額架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但一睇就知幅圖唔係 iphone x</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIphone x 唔會show 電量"},{"pid":"104221414cb95ac8cb64cc627e187fd6e7eba547","tid":469872,"uid":872,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/16/094458_6b0b1d25887499b958da911d31d854a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F16%2F094458_6b0b1d25887499b958da911d31d854a7.jpg&h=54d1c236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我暫時夠 相個啲如果唔夠會買8蚊50GB ICLOUD<br />\n應該夠用"},{"pid":"100650593a70c16e8520c328413e1df8fd035ff9","tid":469872,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:49:11.000Z","msg":"成屋都係idevice 未驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a2c1b0742fca77d1e39ac5efe883f3bee08424","tid":469872,"uid":19854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:49:14.000Z","msg":"我去apple 問左兩次藍精靈<br />\n佢地話icloud 只係sync d 相上去做backup<br />\n唔會慳到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過256 太貴唯有硬食64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bd7575ae83fcae25c93b2456b5f4dab412cd8a","tid":469872,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去apple 問左兩次藍精靈<br />\n佢地話icloud 只係sync d 相上去做backup<br />\n唔會慳到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過256 太貴唯有硬食64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有setting 可以optimised storage,姐係放你啲相/片上iCloud/ 之後轉你部機果啲十年都唔睇嘅相做縮圖，你要edit 佢先download 追張原圖落黎.<br />\n<br />\n(E.g. 我iPhone SE 個mon 連720p都無，其實如果就咁睇唔edit 唔放大大跟本無必要12MP 相。開左optimise 就留一張相對低quality 嘅係到，原圖上返iCloud.咁你iPhone 就會多左位出黎)<br />\n<br />\n不過講到尾其實就係上網data 錢俾多啲定係俾買機錢多啲嘅問題姐。"},{"pid":"922de83081cec6708b6da1d69438960b0545ad2c","tid":469872,"uid":5686,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去apple 問左兩次藍精靈<br />\n佢地話icloud 只係sync d 相上去做backup<br />\n唔會慳到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過256 太貴唯有硬食64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋藍精靈信五成好啦。你問佢間舖有咩賣都未必答到你。問iOS SETTING 呢啲對佢地黎講太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc3caba0e4eb396649929e6daa2fceee6250e1c","tid":469872,"uid":872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去apple 問左兩次藍精靈<br />\n佢地話icloud 只係sync d 相上去做backup<br />\n唔會慳到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過256 太貴唯有硬食64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋藍精靈信五成好啦。你問佢間舖有咩賣都未必答到你。問iOS SETTING 呢啲對佢地黎講太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家啲藍精靈真係on撚9<br />\n連個客都熟過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}